{"tid":1881051,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"聶德權：相比2003年 現時社會氣氛不同 令抗疫更困難","createTime":"2020-02-15T09:32:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-20T10:41:43.000Z","uid":212626,"like":7,"dislike":110,"uniUserReply":61,"replies":[{"pid":"c9c0abd0e2e994b27f41eb344075f2de10420264","tid":1881051,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:32:39.000Z","msg":"【Now新聞台】約二千多名港人仍然滯留湖北，政制及內地事務局局長聶德權指，若本港有足夠檢疫設施，或可分批接送滯留港人，又指現時社會對政府信任度低，令抗疫難度增加。<br />\n<br />\n2200多名港人滯留湖北，回港無期。政制及內地事務局局長聶德權指，這批港人分散三十多個城市，要制定方案將他們集中，過程要顧及感染風險，加上香港的檢疫中心接近爆滿，需要先增加檢疫設施，才有機會分批接送滯留港人。<br />\n<br />\n香港2003年已有抗疫經驗，但聶德權認為，現時社會氣氛不同，令抗疫更困難。<br />\n<br />\n現時滯留湖北的港人，有十人確診，一名62歲女子情況嚴重。聶德權指，政府無一早公布，是因為當地情況對香港公共衛生無影響。<br />\n<br />\n另外，聶德權被問到港澳辦改組，他表示，今次的人事公布是架構調整，認為中央堅持一國兩制方針不變。<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=380679\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380679&d=uD1rvIJwXfBqs1i1iclFx%2F5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=7063617e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.now.com%2Fhome%2Flocal%2Fplayer%3FnewsId%3D380679&h=31153d79\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.now.com/home/local/player?newsId=380679</a>"},{"pid":"2ff84759f248d24f2b3a51faace2a45f42f309bc","tid":1881051,"uid":212626,"like":36,"dislike":29,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:34:00.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/GfZ1odT.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGfZ1odT.png&h=6de6b0ac&s={SIZE}\" /> <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/H1zTYNd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FH1zTYNd.png&h=81c67dce&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n果然係柒婆親信<br />\n柒婆一定係咁樣諗<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e230db8414da409f7c0105197c0ff32bda3db98c","tid":1881051,"uid":212626,"like":3,"dislike":5,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-02-15T09:34:35.000Z","msg":"聶德權認為，與2003年沙士(SARS)比較，現時政府應對武漢肺炎疫情